# {{ project_name }} — documentation

This tree follows the [Irminsul](https://github.com/{{ github_user }}/irminsul) layout.

| Layer | What lives here |
|-------|-----------------|
| `00-foundation/` | Principles, constraints, stakeholders. Rarely change. |
| `10-architecture/` | System overview, containers, boundaries, deployment. |
| `20-components/` | One doc per component. Most edits live here. |
| `30-workflows/` | Cross-component how-it-works narratives. |
| `40-reference/` | Generated. Schemas, API surface, error catalog. Don't hand-edit. |
| `50-decisions/` | ADRs. Append-only. |
| `60-operations/` | Runbooks, playbooks, SLOs, on-call. |
| `70-knowledge/` | Tutorials, how-tos, explanations. |
| `80-evolution/` | Roadmap, RFCs, risks, deprecations. |
| `90-meta/` | Docs about the doc system itself. |

See [`CONTRIBUTING.md`](CONTRIBUTING.md) for how to write docs in this system, and [`GLOSSARY.md`](GLOSSARY.md) for canonical vocabulary.
